This type of application should be completed by all who seek any position that will involve the supervision and/or custody of children or youth. You should tailor the application to the specific circumstances in your congregation. However, the employment application should include sections for personal identification, job qualifications, experience and background for the past 5-10 years, references, a criminal history, and a waiver/consent to a periodic criminal records check or fingerprinting.

a whole lot of fun!
Since 2007, Our goal is building you a safe space to eat, drink, watch sports, and have fun! We are more than your local bar! We are a community that ensures an awesome experience, great service, and a whole lot of fun! Open 11am Daily, come check out our delicious lunch specials, with a crisp, cold beer for Happy hour! We have over 40 Big screen t.v’s to make sure you never have to miss a second of your favorite game! We take pride in being a smoke-free, friendly atmosphere, with nightly events and specials! At Rack èm up, we are not just a bar, it’s a destination!
Meet the All-Stars Behind Rackem Up Sports Bar!
Get to know the powerhouse team that brings the energy to Rackem Up Sports Bar. Our squad is passionate about creating an unforgettable experience for every guest. From the mixologists crafting your favorite drinks to the chefs serving up winning bites, our team is here to ensure that every visit to Rackem Up is a victory. Meet the faces that make the game-day magic happen – we’re not just a team; we’re family, and we can’t wait to welcome you to ours!
Join our team
General Manager
I believe the only way to be truly fulfilled, is by doing what you believe is great work. Being in the service industry for almost a decade, Working with a supportive team, in an environment that interests and inspires you to learn is extremely essential. That is why I am the upmost grateful to be apart of the Rack family the past 4 years. Rack is much more than a sports bar to me, It’s my second home.
Assistant Manager
Hi, I’m Shannon — Assistant Manager at Rack Em Up, Jacksonville’s go-to spot for cold beer, big games, and even better vibes. With a background in hospitality and a serious love for keeping things running smooth (and fun!), I thrive in the fast-paced buzz of game nights, happy hours, and everything in between.

I’m all about making people feel at home—whether it’s remembering your go-to order, cheering on your team with you, or helping turn a regular night out into a great story. Since moving to Jacksonville in Summer 2024, Rack has become more than just my workplace—it’s my community, my second home, and the best place to catch me in my element.
Shift Supervisor
I’ve been behind the bar at Rack ’Em Up Sports Bar for the past two years, and it’s been one unforgettable ride. From pouring drinks to sharing laughs, I’ve met some of the most amazing people along the way. I’m all about good energy, great conversations, and making sure everyone feels right at home. Whether it’s game night or just a night out, I’ve got your drink ready and your vibe covered.
We Are Committed to Exceptional Customer Service and Getting the Job Done Right!
At Rackem Up Sports Bar, our commitment to exceptional customer service is unwavering. We take pride in going above and beyond to ensure that every guest’s experience exceeds expectations. From the moment you walk through our doors, our dedicated team is focused on creating a welcoming atmosphere where you can relax, enjoy, and celebrate. We believe in getting the job done right, whether it’s crafting the perfect cocktail, serving up a delicious meal, or providing prompt and attentive service. Your satisfaction is our priority, and we are dedicated to making every visit to Rackem Up memorable and enjoyable. Cheers to excellence, and thank you for choosing us as your sports destination!
Score Big Moments, Visit Rackem Up Today!
Ready to elevate your sports-watching game? Join us at Rackem Up Sports Bar, where every visit is a victory celebration. Bring your friends, cheer for your team, and indulge in the best of drinks and camaraderie.
VISIT US TODAY!
